    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that makes sense, but i want to dig deeper into the disincentive side. if you look at the data from the last decade, wouldn't you say there's a pretty clear correlation between certain benefit increases and a drop in people looking for work? it seems like a pretty direct cause-and-effect for a lot of industries.",
